This is my first Project is use laragon and phpmyadmin for database management. I have created a database named "lalagon_db" and I want to connect it to my PHP application using PDO. The configuration file (config.php) contains the necessary credentials to establish the connection.

Here is an example of how your config.php file should look to connect to the "lalagon_db" database using PDO:

```php
<?php
$servername = "localhost";
$username = "root"; 
$password = ""; // Leave this empty if you haven't set a password for the root user
$dbname = "lalagon_db"; // The name of your database

try {
    $conn = new PDO("mysql:host=$servername;dbname=$dbname", $username, $password);
    // set the PDO error mode to exception
    $conn->setAttribute(PDO::ATTR_ERRMODE, PDO::ERRMODE_EXCEPTION);
    echo "Connected successfully"; 
} catch(PDOException $e) {
    echo "Connection failed: " . $e->getMessage();
}